#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into"
" a tool to manage your entire workflow."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຖືກລວມເຂົ້າເປັນແອັບດຽວຢ່າງສົມບູນ. ດາວໂຫຼດເພື່ອປ່ຽນໂທລະສັບຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັນເຄື່ອງມືໃນການຈັດການທຸກ"
"ຂັ້ນຕອນການເຮັດວຽກ."

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
